lead_paragraph: Hillary Clinton has faced relentless speculation over her White House aspirations, but it took "Daily Show" host Jon Stewart a matter of minutes on Tuesday night to conclude using a satirical "career-aptitude test" she was campaign-ready.

headline.main: Comedian Jon Stewart Tells Hillary Clinton 'You've Declared Already'
headline.print_headline: Comedian Jon Stewart Tells Hillary Clinton 'You've Declared Already'
